data.text:
Ghostbusters II

Directed by Ivan Reitman. Starring Bill Murray, Dan Aykroyd, Sigourney Weaver, Harold Ramis, Rick Moranis, Annie Potts. The ghostbusters attempt to rid New York City from the slime and negative energy that plagues it.
